git commit -m "Initial commit"
git remote add origin https://github.com/rgokulnath24/my-first-react-app.git
git push -u origin main



To View the FrontEnd Static Project:

for each React project, you should run:

1.npm install gh-pages --save-dev

2.Inside package.json, under "scripts" section, add these lines:

"deploy": "gh-pages -d dist" in package.json

||=>When I run npm run deploy, take everything inside the dist folder and upload it to GitHub Pages using the gh-pages tool. Upload the contents of this specific directory to GitHub Pages

